external_knowledge:
- 'leafy treasures' refers to products categorized as 'Herbs'; 
- 'canopy' metaphorically represents the product category; 
- 'flourished' refers to being sold; 
- 'opening quarter of 2023' refers to the first quarter of the year 2023; 
- 'bounty of their harvest' refers to the sales quantity; 
- 'wealth they've sown' refers to the total revenue generated from sales; 
- 'from the most fruitful to the least' means the results should be ordered by total revenue in descending order.

sql:
SELECT products.product_name, suppliers.supplier_name
FROM products
INNER JOIN suppliers ON products.supplier_id = suppliers.supplier_id;
